0.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------

New features
- API changed: * KDcraw destructor is now virtual.
               * Added DcrawSettingsContainer destructor.
               * Separate embedded JPEG preview extraction and half decoding methods
                 to get a preview of RAW pictures.
		 
